  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/uncategorized/\u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0db1-\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7-\u0da7\u0dd3-\u0d91\u0db1\u0dca-\u0d92--\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca-\u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2/1-394868",
  "time_ut": 1656310482,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0da7\u0dd3.\u0d91\u0db1\u0dca.\u0d92. \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "TNA presents Anura's Jaffna conference Leaders are coming too",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the National People's Force Anura Kumara Dissanayake said in Jaffna that the US case against Sri Lanka was similar to the atomic bomb dropped on Japan.",
        "Mr. Anura Kumara was addressing a gathering of participants at the National People's Force District Conference held at a private hotel in Jaffna on the 25th evening.",
        "Mavai Senathirajah, Leader of the Illangai Tamil Arusakachchi Party, Dharmalingam Siddharthan, Leader of the PLOTE, Suresh Premachandran, Leader of the EPRLF, CVK, Former Chairman of the Provincial Council were present on the occasion. Mr. Sivagnanam and many members of the Jaffna District National People's Force participated.",
        "Addressing the gathering, the Leader of the National People's Force Anura Kumara further said,",
        "\u2018People are suffering the most difficult setback in our country today. This is not a natural disaster. This is a situation created by bad governance. Today we are in danger of our children dying before our eyes. Oil imports have come to a complete standstill. The petrol and diesel ship that the Minister of Fuel had said was coming to Sri Lanka has now headed towards India.",
        "An American bank has filed a lawsuit against the Sri Lankan government. The government says the loans will not be repaid. Proponents of her case have been working to make the actual transcript of this statement available online. That it was similar to the atomic bomb dropped on Hiroshima and Nagasaki in Japan. As a result, the whole country and the economy have collapsed. \u201d"
      ],
